metadata.name: Memory Lane: The First Hue
metadata.description:
Memory Lane: The Hues

What has not been erased by the waves of time  
Continues to live on as a memory in our hearts, 
Accompanying our journey before the world ends.

Some of these forgotten moments resurface,  
From time to time.

Like the canvas of an awaited sunset,  
They often begin with a single detail. 
An emotion. 
A complexity.  
A hue.
